{"tid":1287810,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"見到畫家被捕，有感而發","createTime":"2019-07-05T11:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T03:38:06.000Z","uid":132544,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc0204e855a0d79c55bf2dca6b110fa00cd732c","tid":1287810,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"七一發夢當日，因為家人擔心，我十點就夢醒啦。<br />\n夢醒途中，遇到畫家，我倆面面相覷，<br />\n佢突然走過嚟同我講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「我入去買汽水炸！」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講，見到畫家，個心又驚又喜，<br />\n雖然佢係白卡，對個行動好有幫助，<br />\n但係都好擔心佢會出事。<br />\n我係個00後，無去魚蛋革命旺角街頭，<br />\n我都係發夢圍警總先初曉畫家哩個人，<br />\n見佢瘋瘋癲癲，做啲野又鳩下鳩下，<br />\n都幾佩服佢。<br />\n<br />\n佢好神氣咁同我交談後，就走咗入立法會啦。<br />\n<br />\n直到頭先，我睇到哩個post<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔好笑！畫家落淚！拘捕時期經歷咗啲咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1287486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1287486</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我成個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回想當時發夢，畫家神氣中帶傻，<br />\n依加望住鏡頭流淚，<br />\n到底黑警係哩段期間對佢做咗啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母死黑警</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ae5cef24b0f4a1a42c3adb399cde1076c0f235","tid":1287810,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:10:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17d0ce169ca2b0c9c2df840c38fb6ce14933f32","tid":1287810,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"有鏡頭都7警打<br />\n<br />\n冇鏡頭唔敢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有人話咩警察都有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a46da3db6c0c4ab2b2be12af1e53632182a4fcf","tid":1287810,"uid":132544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"要教返畫家出嚟呀"},{"pid":"62fe28e6036dfac051c0fcb00199f7f36c64709d","tid":1287810,"uid":132544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要救返畫家出嚟呀</blockquote>"},{"pid":"33c6df89d6c2772b23e4c50723f3d5bfe2247652","tid":1287810,"uid":132544,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c17d0ce169ca2b0c9c2df840c38fb6ce14933f32","tid":1287810,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"有鏡頭都7警打<br />\n<br />\n冇鏡頭唔敢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有人話咩警察都有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"聽講佢仲比人玩撚<br />\n屌你老母真係笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852e84c5781fea1359caf7c52b12db867f068c99","tid":1287810,"uid":77084,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"我好擔心佢，我自己都係精神病患者，見到佢個樣咁樣，我非常之難過，被侵犯會需要一段好長時間先可以復原，佢而家仲唔知會點樣，我覺得自己好幸福，到時又好想關心下佢"},{"pid":"d7fc5eca3dc6974879c05b947ef317154b9fd8fe","tid":1287810,"uid":159913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff9b5fdc1808926198db704bc82083cae0fff23","tid":1287810,"uid":132544